notes: 毛宗武, 蒙朝吉 / Mao Zongwu, Meng Chaoji. 畲语简志 / She yu jian zhi (A Sketch of She). Beijing:  	民族出版社: 新華書店发行 / Min zu chu ban she: Xin hua shu dian fa xing, 1986.This dialect of She is spoken in Lianhua (莲花), Huidong County (惠东县), Guangdong, China.Tones:1 = /22/2 = /53/3 = /33/4 = /42/5 = /31/6 = /35/7 = /21/8 = /54/
